data.description: Perfect place to live.  Perfect place to entertain.  Affordable and conveniently located to shopping, dining, and all East Nashville has to offer!  Completely renovated and updated.  Move in Ready.  Two driveways, private fenced backyard, covered porch, open patios, and two sheds.  Kitchen has additional cabinets with stainless appliances & gas range.  Sun room & extra bonus areas.  All space has been turned into functional spaces to live. Great place to make your home!
